metadata.title: Mark Recovery Program Commercial Biological Sampling (Canada)
metadata.description:
Parameter
Biological data on individual salmon sampled from all major commercial fisheries

Measurement Details
Biological samples are collected to determine age-class, catch structure, cohort recruitment, age/size interrelationships, gear selectivity and growth rates in salmonids coastal British Columbia.

[ A TCODE project ]
